      • attributeAdded

        public void attributeAdded(ServletContextAttributeEvent event)
        Receives notification that an attribute has been added to the ServletContext. The call will be forwarded to the same method with no arguments defined on the subclasses
        Specified by:
        attributeAdded in interface ServletContextAttributeListener
        Parameters:
        event - the ServletContextAttributeEvent containing the ServletContext to which the attribute was added, along with the attribute name and value
